WITH history as (
            INSERT INTO task_log(task_id,
                                 warehouse_id,
                                 queue_name,
                                 task_data,
                                 status,
                                 entity_id,
                                 entity_type,
                                 message,
                                 attempt,
                                 started_at,
                                 duration,
                                 progress,
                                 execution_details,
                                 attempt_scheduled_for,
                                 last_heartbeat_at,
                                 parent_task_id,
                                 task_created_at)
                SELECT task_id,
                       warehouse_id,
                       queue_name,
                       task_data,
                       $3,
                       entity_id,
                       entity_type,
                       $2,
                       attempt,
                       picked_up_at,
                       now() AT TIME ZONE 'UTC' - picked_up_at,
                       1.0000,
                       execution_details,
                       scheduled_for,
                       last_heartbeat_at,
                       parent_task_id,
                       created_at
                FROM task
                WHERE task_id = $1)
        DELETE FROM task
        WHERE task_id = $1
